The cheese was gooey, the chicken flavorful and overall great taste, the service I received was just as good. My second trip to Corky's I ordered the hardest to find dish in my opinion, a good diner style plate of Steak and Mashed Potatoes. So many places have let me down in this regard with dry flavorless steak and flavorless mash. Corky's gave me a succulent, juicy steak packed with flavor and potatoes covered in delicious gravy.
